file.name: openapi.yaml
file.content:
---
openapi: 3.0.3
info:
  title: rspec-openapi
  version: 1.0.0
servers: []
paths:
  "/roda":
    post:
      summary: POST /roda
      requestBody:
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              type: object
              properties:
                id:
                  type: integer
            example:
              id: 1
      responses:
        '200':
          description: when id is given it returns 200
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: object
                properties:
                  id:
                    type: integer
                  name:
                    type: string
              example:
                id: 1
                name: hello
